Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.32,0:02:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,All the pirates who are after the One Piece...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.72,0:02:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,...head for the New World, the second half of the Grand Line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.99,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,However, no one has ever fully explored it except for Gold Roger, the Pirate King.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.33,0:03:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The New World has ruined many pirates' dreams and ambitions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.38,0:03:17.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.38,0:03:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and his friends venture into that sea.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.02,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna become the Pirate King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.66,0:03:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,On their way to the New World,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.19,0:03:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy and his crew reached Fishman Island located 10,000 meters below sea level,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.96,0:03:38.60,Default,,0,0,0,,where the New Fishman Pirates who are looking to destroy the Ryugu Kingdom...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.60,0:03:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,...assisted by Vander Decken, who is after Shirahoshi, are engaging in secret maneuvers.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.41,0:03:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,The Straw Hats find themselves caught up in the turmoil.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.08,0:03:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,This country will soon be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.11,0:03:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And it will be rebuilt under a new king.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.75,0:03:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Namely, me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.19,0:03:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Citizens of Fishman Island!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,It's time to say goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.03,0:04:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,...to the old Ryugu Kingdom!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.96,0:04:08.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Three hours from now, at Conchcorde Plaza,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to cut this incompetent King's head off!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.60,0:04:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.97,0:04:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll show you something good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.51,0:04:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you are somewhere on the island watching this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.78,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You people shattered Arlong's dream - he was a symbol of Fishmen's anger.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.25,0:04:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zoro! Usopp! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.76,0:04:35.66,Default,,0,0,0,,--What fools... --I can't believe they got caught!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.16,0:04:39.33,Default,,0,0,0,,--It's water! --It's water!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.80,0:04:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,That room will be filled with water by the time we finish executing the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.60,0:04:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,You lowly creatures can't survive that, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.44,0:04:54.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark! Take me to the Ryugu Palace!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Wait," Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.78,0:04:57.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.58,0:05:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You people shouldn't fight Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.72,0:05:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe! They have my crew!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.12,0:05:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And I got to do something about Hody before my friends get into real trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.82,0:05:09.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.26,0:05:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop me if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.13,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't let my guard down just because we fought together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I almost forgot that you're that man's brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.84,0:05:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You ready to do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.42,0:05:41.39,B1,,0,0,0,,{\fad(2000,2000)}"A Rift Opens Up! Luffy vs. Jinbe!"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.84,0:05:57.04,Default,,0,0,0,,People called me The Submarine of the East Blue when I was a kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.04,0:05:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I can easily swim across even a twenty-five meter pool!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.28,0:06:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I can run that far!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.75,0:06:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't swim but I can run!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.85,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Brook! Let's see which one of us is faster sometime soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't beat me! I'm going to run beyond the horizon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.80,0:06:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, it doesn't look good, does it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.60,0:06:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it doesn't! The surface of the water is getting closer!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,--Look, look! The water is... --It's coming! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.81,0:06:30.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.17,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What's your problem?! How can you be so calm?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Do you have any ideas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.22,0:06:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.35,0:06:43.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--Don't be so honest! --That's so clear, I like it. Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.42,0:06:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,If only I had my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.86,0:06:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Sword? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.89,0:06:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.76,0:06:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to do it in front of you two...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.80,0:06:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What is "it"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.97,0:07:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Dorororororo...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.64,0:07:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone, bone, bone, bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.81,0:07:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Brook, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.18,0:07:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Bone, bone, bone, bone...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.51,0:07:11.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Brook!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.48,0:07:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Bang!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.56,0:07:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.10,0:07:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, see you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.97,0:07:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, w-wait, wait, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.00,0:07:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You got some explaining to do!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do something like that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.78,0:07:42.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I can make my soul leave my body.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.55,0:07:44.92,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just like a real dead person.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.92,0:07:46.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.72,0:07:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It happened when I was on my world tour as Soul King...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.89,0:07:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I was in quite a slump at that time for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:08:01.30,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(1000,1000)}TDS SALES PLUMMET---- CONCERT TICKETS REMAIN UNSOLD
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.46,0:08:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sales of TDs and concert tickets were dropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.40,0:08:03.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And I didn't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:07.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Today's concert was not so great.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.67,0:08:10.51,Default,,0,0,0,,He's not making great music lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't feel his soul!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.41,0:08:18.12,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened to you, Brook? Write a new song that will sell!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.82,0:08:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not that easy to make a hit song...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.82,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Music is something much more sublime.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.03,0:08:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe... Maybe, the God of Music doesn't love me anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,One more time... Just one more song is fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.30,0:08:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,God! God of Music!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:47.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Bless me with a melody that will shake everybody to their soul! God!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.42,0:09:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.72,0:09:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! What is going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.93,0:09:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Since I got this ability, I noticed what's missing in my songs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.37,0:09:14.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I found a way out of my slump!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.97,0:09:17.17,Default,,0,0,0,,--What was it? --Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you had the ability to pass undetected through walls...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.15,0:09:29.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any able-bodied male understands the potential, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:34.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm jealous, Zoro! I wish I were him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.96,0:09:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.99,0:09:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the water got that high!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-chin! Boss Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.22,0:10:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy! Jinbe! Hold on a second! What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.02,0:10:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna go to the Ryugu Palace to save my crew and kick that Hody guy's ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.33,0:10:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Don't do it"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.83,0:10:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey hey, why do you have to fight now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.80,0:10:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.50,0:10:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama! Boss Jinbe-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.14,0:10:22.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Shark! Take me! To the Ryugu Place!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.31,0:10:25.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I said "Wait"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.21,0:10:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Outta my way!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.68,0:10:30.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Fishman Karate--Shark Brick Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.16,Default,,0,0,0,,--What?! --Luffy-chin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.16,0:10:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow... Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.87,0:10:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,It worked?! He's supposed to be immune to blows like that as a rubber man!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.11,0:11:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The Fishman Karate is all about manipulating the water around you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.48,0:11:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The shock wave can travel through water vapor in the air
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.48,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,and through to the water within your target's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Every living thing is made up of water. So even a rubber man can't escape the impact!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.50,0:11:26.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.81,0:11:31.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let you go, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.18,0:11:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Gear 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.14,0:11:36.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.85,0:11:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,...Jet Stamp!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.46,0:11:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this all you learned from your training?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't bet on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.80,0:11:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.80,0:11:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.90,0:12:02.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.01,0:12:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, move aside, Robin!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.94,0:12:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Who are you?! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.34,0:12:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Robin-chan's in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.30,0:12:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.00,0:12:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the reason but you two are friends, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.11,0:12:38.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?! Why did Robin come out of the forest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.44,0:12:42.71,OS,,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)}WATERWHEEL TOWN
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.02,0:12:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,J-Just give up! You guys can't win!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.66,0:13:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,No way. Didn't you see Boss Hody's broadcast?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.30,0:13:09.21,Default,,0,0,0,,This country will be destroyed. And Neptune is gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.21,0:13:10.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.41,0:13:11.91,Default,,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.64,0:13:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't kill them.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.61,0:13:18.15,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do so, you'll be no better than them!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.15,0:13:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.58,0:13:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryuboshi, Manboshi, take them into custody.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.72,0:13:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,--I got it-so-la-ti-do! --Count on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.39,0:13:30.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're as indulgent as before-dosun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.76,0:13:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Does indulgence run in the Neptune family's blood?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.93,0:13:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You are not just getting back at humans but hurting your fellow beings.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.34,0:13:44.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Doesn't it pain your heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Any Fishman who sides with humans deserves death-dosun!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.65,0:13:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Lead the way for your father--towards death! Fukaboshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.79,0:13:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Screw you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.65,0:14:26.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.02,0:14:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,They did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.02,0:14:34.42,Default,,0,0,0,,They got the New Fishman Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.92,0:14:38.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the 3 great royal brothers could do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.33,0:14:40.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Fukaboshi-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.40,0:14:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the rest up to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.13,0:14:44.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.63,0:14:48.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to Conchcorde Plaza to save our father!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.74,0:14:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,All right. Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.92,0:15:01.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go to the execution ground.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.95,0:15:04.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you want some of us to stay here at the palace,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.29,0:15:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss Hody?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.02,0:15:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:12.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This Ryugu Palace is impregnable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave some men to open the gate when we come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.03,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't want the new king getting locked out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We sure don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.44,0:15:24.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That'd be nonsense-jamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.58,0:15:28.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't win citizens' hearts with violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.41,0:15:34.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You have only a little life left. Say what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.75,0:15:39.59,Default,,0,0,0,,This hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.86,0:15:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That stupid swordsman cut me there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.29,0:15:48.20,Default,,0,0,0,,The drug is wearing off. Hey, give me the Energy Steroid.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.20,0:15:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.78,0:16:01.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The pain is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.31,0:16:04.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it okay to take that much at once?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.25,0:16:05.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.28,0:16:09.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Boss, what should we do about those 3 Straw Hats?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.65,0:16:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They're just humans. They'll drown if we leave them like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.49,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,No matter who is coming to save them, no one can break into the palace.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That aside, how are the new residents from the Fishman District doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.67,0:16:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They're doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.24,0:16:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,They're already moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.61,0:16:36.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's good. There'll be empty houses for them.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.21,0:16:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Some will leave the country and the others will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.28,0:16:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,They can just move into those houses.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.09,0:16:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll make a great country in which all citizens can look down on humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.47,0:16:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I found it! The ray of hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.14,0:17:04.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Those Fishmen that we saw earlier are all gone and nobody is here in the palace
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.61,0:17:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,but they left Pappagu-san behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.34,0:17:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,All right then, Brook, ask Pappagu to find the key to unchain us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.42,0:17:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,--And the keys to this cage and this room... --Wait a minute, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.22,0:17:16.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.89,0:17:22.09,Default,,0,0,0,,One of my swords is enough. Just bring my sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll cut them all!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.83,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, you're so reliable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.86,0:17:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, I'll go ask Pappagu-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.38,0:17:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.71,0:17:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell? I thought we were just invited to a banquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if those Straw Hats are doing okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.55,0:17:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Pappagu-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.34,0:18:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,--Pappagu-san... --What? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I found you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Boom!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.35,0:18:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.52,0:18:28.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A ghost!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.90,0:18:36.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.37,0:18:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a ghost--I'm scared!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.27,0:18:41.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Pappagu-san! It's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.24,0:18:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have much time! I need the key... I mean, the sword! Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.58,0:18:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,No, stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.98,0:18:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,--No!! --What do you mean "No"? Listen to me! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.63,0:19:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you okay, you two? And Sanji?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.10,0:19:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Think about it, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.91,0:19:21.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What will happen if you guys resort to violence now on Fishman Island?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.51,0:19:28.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Everytime Fishmen tried to open their hearts to humans, humans disappointed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.22,0:19:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Humans are very violent." "Humans hate and look down on Fishmen."
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.79,0:19:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened in the past planted those twisted ideas in Fishmen's minds.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.27,0:19:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,In the case of Arlong,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.40,0:19:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,many Fishmen believe that humans hunted him because he was a Fishman.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If you, the people who beat Arlong, fight Hody now,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.51,0:19:58.92,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think will happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.92,0:20:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if it helps the island overcome this crisis,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.65,0:20:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing you people knocking down Hody who is standing against humans...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.59,0:20:15.33,Default,,0,0,0,,...would make the islanders to think that things will never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.58,0:20:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Jinbe,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.25,0:20:33.08,Default,,0,0,0,,we have to rescue our crew.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:36.99,Default,,0,0,0,,And if nothing is done, Hody will rule Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.02,0:20:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,We have so many friends on the island.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.36,0:20:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.13,0:20:49.97,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been trying so hard to hide who did that to you
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,but you said a while ago...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.07,0:20:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,...that Hody attacks those Fishmen who are sympathetic to humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.64,0:21:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get beaten by them because you spoke up for us?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.49,0:21:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Hachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.79,0:21:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Hatchin, is that true? Hody and his crew did that to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.46,0:21:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.03,0:21:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.56,0:21:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I think part of the reason Luffy wants to fight is because this is your home.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.80,0:21:32.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard that you helped our captain when he had his back against the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.48,0:21:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't thank you enough for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.22,0:21:51.06,Default,,0,0,0,,And if Luffy wants to fight, we will go along with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.60,0:21:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We can't just leave the island like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,We have reason to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.72,0:22:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,The reason is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.65,0:22:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Camie-chan's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.65,0:22:21.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And Shirahoshi-chan's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.92,0:22:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! This country is the Mermaid paradise of my dreams!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.57,0:22:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Get out of my way, Jinbe! You gotta let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.48,0:22:45.05,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I won't! Leave it up to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.99,0:22:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.12,0:22:56.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Then I'll just beat my way past you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.13,0:22:59.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll fight you as many times as I have to till you understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.26,0:23:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.47,0:23:03.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut it out, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.08,0:23:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Neptune's execution draws ever closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.42,0:23:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Hody's powerful allies are mobilizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.02,0:23:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The New Fishman Pirates are overrunning every part of Fishman Island.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.43,0:23:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,But then, just as his ambition is coming to fruition,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.53,0:23:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,an terrifying change befalls Hody!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.30,0:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.80,0:23:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,"Something Has Happened to Hody! The True Power of the Evil Drug!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.07,0:23:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
